        {type:"discuss",prompt:"读读《浪淘沙》（其一），说说你从哪里体会到了黄河的磅礴气势。",promptEn:"Read 'Waves of Sand' and tell where you feel the Yellow River's mighty power."},
        {type:"discuss",prompt:"想想《江南春》抓住哪些景物写出了江南春天的特点。",promptEn:"Think about which scenes in 'Spring in Jiangnan' capture the features of spring in the south."},
        {type:"discover",prompt:"读读下面的诗句，说说你发现了什么。\n一水护田将绿绕，\n两山排闼送青来。",promptEn:"Read these lines and say what you notice about the use of personification:\n'One stream guards the fields...'\n'Two hills push open the gate...'"}
